headline.print_headline: European Security Body Negotiating to Recover Plane Victims-Dutch PM
headline.main: European Security Body Negotiating to Recover Plane Victims-Dutch PM

lead_paragraph: Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte said the Organisation for Security and Co-operation in Europe was negotiating with separatists to bring a train containing bodies from the Malaysia Airlines disaster under Ukrainian government control.
